 to say I'm back.

547
00:32:43,195 --> 00:32:45,497
And... to tell you something.

548
00:32:47,333 --> 00:32:49,201
I guess it must've been
 a pretty rough tour, huh?

549
00:32:49,301 --> 00:32:52,638
