Or a housewife.

574
00:34:09,081 --> 00:34:11,250
A housewife?

575
00:34:11,750 --> 00:34:12,784
Housewife.

576
00:34:12,884 --> 00:34:16,688
You know, sleep-in maid.

577
00:34:16,788 --> 00:34:19,091
I don't... I don't follow you.

578
00:34:19,191 --> 00:34:21,893
It was a joke. [laughs]

579
